{"tid":778942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FB將免費播西甲！","createTime":"2018-08-14T05:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T05:28:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e71c7b7f94555d4229ddf721fa81284d7971e0e8","tid":778942,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"但只限印度大陸&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nFacebook印度取得西甲轉播權！Facebook將容許其於印度大陸用戶免費觀看未來三季賽事，西甲指，新一個球季於本周五開始，全數380場賽事，均可讓印度、阿富汗、孟加拉、不丹、尼泊爾、馬爾代夫、斯里蘭卡及巴基斯坦觀眾觀看。<br />\n<br />\n西甲數碼策略部主管Afredo Bermejo表示，於過去兩年，該會其中一個目標就是將球賽推廣予更廣大的受眾，而與免費平台如FB合作，其印度2.7億用戶對於西甲來說是非常重要。<br />\nFB及西甲均未有就今次合作提供相關財務數據，而Sony Picture於當地擁有201-2018賽季西甲賽事轉播權，當時作價3200萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180814/58560632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58560632&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=65ddc60e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58560632&h=3d8fea61\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180814/58560632</a>"},{"pid":"e27dedf27080068ac33334b0311239e03c4b0431","tid":778942,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"vpn?"},{"pid":"9c3e38aaff3bdf051a541d7ee3cd107d02cf63e5","tid":778942,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e27dedf27080068ac33334b0311239e03c4b0431","tid":778942,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"vpn?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"用得vpn上網睇<br />\n用link睇仲容易啦<br />\n仲有英文聽"}]}